    <div class='update_description'><i onclick="document.location='23482#1418676399'; reset_anchor();" class="pull-right icon icon-share"></i><div class="header"><time datetime="2014-12-15T20:46:39+00:00">Dec 15, 2014 08:46 PM UTC</time> by <b>Tim Cartwright</b><a class="anchor" name="1418676399">&nbsp;</a></div><pre>I noted your willingness to test EL 7 support and will close this ticket. Thanks!</pre></div><div class='update_description'><i onclick="document.location='23482#1418674740'; reset_anchor();" class="pull-right icon icon-share"></i><div class="header"><time datetime="2014-12-15T20:19:00+00:00">Dec 15, 2014 08:19 PM UTC</time><a class="anchor" name="1418674740">&nbsp;</a></div><pre><font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;much depends on your timelines,</font>

